How you handle it is your business.

563
00:37:58,600 --> 00:38:00,130
Let me tell you, Ms. Liu Wei.

564
00:38:00,720 --> 00:38:02,180
Before Mrs. Qin recovers,

565
00:38:02,600 --> 00:38:04,130
I won't leave the hospital.

566
00:38:05,560 --> 00:38:06,520
Like I said,

567
00:38:06,520 --> 00:38:08,180
we have nothing to talk about.

568
00:38:14,400 --> 00:38:16,440
Fine. Remember this.

569
00:38:17,360 --> 00:38:18,560
We'll see about that.

570
00:38:21,880 --> 00:38:23,540
Close the door for me, please.

571
00:38:33,360 --> 00:38:34,000
Director.

572
00:38:34,720 --> 00:38:37,240
We'll gather all your proposals

573
00:38:37,600 --> 00:38:40,560
and decide on one after thorough review.

574
00:38:45,760 --> 00:38:46,960
Here's another proposal

575
00:38:46,960 --> 00:38:48,290
for everyone to review.

576
00:39:01,680 --> 00:39:02,810
Hello, Manager Liu.

577
00:39:03,840 --> 00:39:05,760
Manager Qin has authorized the signature.

578
00:39:05,760 --> 00:39:06,820
Are you at the bank?

579
00:39:07,080 --> 00:39:08,320
I'm already here.

580
00:39:09,240 --> 00:39:10,640
I'm waiting for you.

581
00:39:11,640 --> 00:39:14,100
Did you bring all the documents and the seal?

582
00:39:14,480 --> 00:39:15,540
I have everything.

583
00:39:16,360 --> 00:39:18,620
Good. I'll be there soon. See you in a bit.

584
00:39:18,800 --> 00:39:19,960
I'll be waiting.

585
00:39:52,840 --> 00:39:53,900
What's happening?

586
00:39:54,680 --> 00:39:56,720
The patient's vital signs are dropping.

587
00:39:56,720 --> 00:39:58,650
Breathing is becoming difficult.

588
00:40:05,320 --> 00:40:06,400
Prepare for surgery immediately.

589
00:40:06,400 --> 00:40:06,800
OK.

590
00:40:12,400 --> 00:40:13,200
Director Chen

591
00:40:13,920 --> 00:40:14,640
Dr. Chen

592
00:40:14,720 --> 00:40:15,560
Director Chen

593
00:40:16,080 --> 00:40:17,080
What happened to my mother?

594
00:40:17,080 --> 00:40:18,440
Your mother's condition has worsened.

595
00:40:18,440 --> 00:40:20,040
She needs immediate surgery.

596
00:40:20,040 --> 00:40:22,440
Has Professor Wei from America arrived?

597
00:40:22,440 --> 00:40:24,970
It's too late. We probably can't wait for him.

598
00:40:25,000 --> 00:40:27,460
Director Chen, can you perform the surgery?

599
00:40:27,640 --> 00:40:28,700
I'm afraid I can't.

600
00:40:29,400 --> 00:40:29,960
Dr. Chen

601
00:40:30,880 --> 00:40:32,200
I beg you.

602
00:40:32,600 --> 00:40:34,600
Please, I beg you to save my mother.

603
00:40:34,760 --> 00:40:35,690
I'm begging you.

604
00:40:35,720 --> 00:40:37,680
Please don't give up. I'm begging you.

605
00:40:37,680 --> 00:40:39,040
We'll do our best.

606
00:40:42,120 --> 00:40:42,920
Xinxin

607
00:40:43,440 --> 00:40:44,640
Let me tell you something.

608
00:40:44,640 --> 00:40:46,600
I'm afraid I can't perform this surgery.

609
00:40:46,600 --> 00:40:48,860
But there's someone who might be able to.

610
00:40:49,040 --> 00:40:49,560
Who?

611
00:40:49,920 --> 00:40:50,650
Come with me.

612
00:40:54,960 --> 00:40:55,640
Hua Ming.

613
00:41:02,760 --> 00:41:04,020
When did you come back?

614
00:41:05,320 --> 00:41:06,040
Xinxin.

615
00:41:08,640 --> 00:41:10,570
Now is not the time to discuss this.

616
00:41:11,600 --> 00:41:13,960
Qin Fenglan is in critical condition. She needs surgery immediately.

617
00:41:13,960 --> 00:41:15,040
Huaming,

618
00:41:15,040 --> 00:41:15,400
Zhongxin Health,

619
00:41:15,400 --> 00:41:16,320
in the hospital now,

620
00:41:16,320 --> 00:41:16,680
Zhongxin Health,

621
00:41:16,680 --> 00:41:18,600
you're the only one we can count on.

622
00:41:18,600 --> 00:41:19,160
Senior.

623
00:41:20,520 --> 00:41:22,360
You know I'm not in the right condition to perform surgery.

624
00:41:22,360 --> 00:41:22,760
Zhongxin Health,

625
00:41:22,760 --> 00:41:23,800
there's no time left.

626
00:41:23,800 --> 00:41:24,800
Zhongxin Health,

627
00:41:24,800 --> 00:41:27,320
Wan Xinxin, please help me convince him.

628
00:41:27,960 --> 00:41:29,290
I'll call Professor Wei

629
00:41:29,440 --> 00:41:30,840
to confirm some details.

630
00:41:31,320 --> 00:41:32,160
This surgery

631
00:41:33,880 --> 00:41:35,280
must be performed by him.

632
00:41:36,000 --> 00:41:37,800
Otherwise Mrs. Qin's condition

633
00:41:38,000 --> 00:41:39,460
will truly be beyond help.

634
00:41:45,800 --> 00:41:47,800
Thank you for coming back this time.

635
00:41:49,080 --> 00:41:51,960
Is the surgical plan ready?

636
00:41:52,480 --> 00:41:53,160
Xinxin.

637
00:41:54,520 --> 00:41:57,280
Dr. Wei has shown me the case.

638
00:41:58,040 --> 00:42:00,800
He says Mrs. Qin's case is quite unusual.

639
00:42:01,240 --> 00:42:02,880
The surgery carries extreme risks.

640
00:42:02,880 --> 00:42:05,410
The patient could die on the operating table.

641
00:42:05,760 --> 00:42:07,800
But Mrs. Qin is in critical condition now.

642
00:42:07,800 --> 00:42:09,600
There are no other options left.

643
00:42:09,760 --> 00:42:12,240
Director Chen says you're the expert in this field.

644
00:42:12,240 --> 00:42:14,600
You're the only one who can save her now.

645
00:42:14,880 --> 00:42:16,400
Xinxin, don't you understand

646
00:42:16,400 --> 00:42:17,840
surgery isn't a game?

647
00:42:18,560 --> 00:42:20,490
Mrs. Qin has helped many patients.

648
00:42:20,960 --> 00:42:22,800
I wish I could help her, but...

649
00:42:22,800 --> 00:42:26,000
But I'm not in the right condition to perform surgery now.

650
00:42:27,000 --> 00:42:27,640
Huaming.

651
00:42:29,560 --> 00:42:30,490
Could you please

652
00:42:32,040 --> 00:42:34,920
do this surgery for me?

653
00:43:45,520 --> 00:43:45,840
Li

654
00:43:48,000 --> 00:43:48,160
Li Wenwang

